Title: Servicenow: Notification plugin
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: notifications
Date: 1552645826
Edition: cee
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 2
State: unknown
Version: 2.0.0i1

Check_MK now supports integration with Servicenow.
You can create, update and close incidents for Host and Service Problems.

The user, used for login, has to have at least the role "itil" in servicenow.
It is recommended to use the same user for caller, which is used for login.

Please see the inline help of the notification method rule within wato for
detailed options.

CMK-1167
